  <div style="text-align: right;"> <span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;"><img alt="Citron Hygiene_With Tag Line_Resized" src="{[devName:Citron_Hygiene_With_Tag_Line_Resize]}" style="max-width: 1289.7199768066405px" title="Citron Hygiene_With Tag Line_Resized" /></span></span> 
